{"tid":1467580,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「咁小事」大家咁小朋友既？","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:24:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:29:25.000Z","uid":63911,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0cee2882bba3747db6a4fdfbd5c06bd0dc652bac","tid":1467580,"uid":63911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:24:15.000Z","msg":"喂人地警察同黑社會合作，對家都當無事啦。對家有無割蓆？<br />\n<br />\n咁細一件事就陣腳大亂？點做大事。<br />\n<br />\n你望下人地啦，出完黑社會，又射爆隻眼，又福建幫。人地都繼續面皮厚，扮無野。<br />\n<br />\n人無恥則無敵。<br />\n你地繼續失民心撚，和平撚。繼續政治潔癖啦，你地咁樣，連普通辦公室政治都輸啦，仲想同共產黨鬥？"},{"pid":"28e05a2d25f6bbb4b8ed37f624a3276716c02714","tid":1467580,"uid":63911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:24:58.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"d362af368c1703fa7f94236694c3e50f8d54c49a","tid":1467580,"uid":63911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:25:34.000Z","msg":"10連"},{"pid":"a01854187a811518b25a266589330162b45d0f05","tid":1467580,"uid":63911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:27:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6799ef4698cf57b57489bc33b4235175ae21af50","tid":1467580,"uid":63911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:27:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9bfc3cf5d9f9b43f2aa0356596be66ea7cce6206","tid":1467580,"uid":67232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:28:02.000Z","msg":"光復香港之前不如先光復連登<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467151\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467151</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8d2557475195a916a158af87fd6518e9ae52774a","tid":1467580,"uid":63911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:28:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af23114deb1d03a4e62f592274a3548ac2d55fec","tid":1467580,"uid":63911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:29:25.000Z","msg":"推"}]}